---
title: Gouda Pork Burgers with Caramelized Sriracha Onion & Smoky Roasted Broccoli
description: These bodacious burgers are positively layered with flavor. First, pork patties are infused with an aromatic mix of garlic, onion, and paprika. Then, the cooked burgers are topped with nutty, melty gouda and a tangle of feisty caramelized onions spiked with sriracha. Everything gets tucked into toasty buns spread with creamy garlic sauce and served with a heap of tender roasted broccoli. Prepare for total taste bud takeover.
